projects.title: Git Fit
projects.description: Git Fit was a fitness website to encourage and offer assistance to individuals wanting to start a healthier lifestyle but needed a helping hand. We offered a macro calculator, fitness and meal plans, and a team of experts to answer any questions. Even people that are well within their fitness journey was welcomed to pre-genereated strength training routines and we has options for maintaining weight as well.

projects.title: Horned Beast
projects.description: This labe provided me with my first opportunity to practive with React components, state, and props, along with conditional rendering and event handling. By the end of the lab, users were ables to click through a working gallery of images that could be filtered based on the number of horns, and interact with the gallery by clicking the images to see a larger version.
